name: Super Toto
description:
Super Toto is a 2D platformer game created on Unity. This game tells about the adventures of Toto. Si Toto must collect coins for provisions and lives to increase life if his life is reduced. Si Toto must pass through enemies, traps, and ravines. If you can't get past it, then Toto will die.

This game is made by:

1. Diffran Nur Cahyo

2. Andri Syaputra
